<b>What's new:</b>
<p>
<ul>
<li>make coordinates view switch between English and metric units
<li>make all charts switch between English and metric units, preserve data for time-based charts, close and reopen static charts
<li>make tools switchable between English and metric units (gps, budget meter, ice thickness)
</ul>
<p>
<b>Not implemented:</b>
<ul>
<li>switching between English/metric units for temperature and snowfall sliders
<li>Experiments tab
<li>Help
</ul>
<p>
<b>Known problems:</b>
<ul>
<li>full-size background image is so large that it exceeds JVM heap space and causes OutOfMemoryException
<li>glacier starts up in steady state, but with no debris or ripple in the ice, and no moraine
</ul>
